{"tid":2356481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：報道指美國或將阿里巴巴和騰訊納入禁止投資中資股名單","createTime":"2021-01-06T23:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T01:28:52.000Z","uid":290404,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"50b1fda64ed8402213ec56538ff1b9b57feb9261","tid":2356481,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:22:05.000Z","msg":"華爾街日報引述消息人士指，美國官員正考慮禁止美國人投資阿里巴巴和騰訊。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，相關計劃仍在審議中，<strong>可能不會通過</strong>，因為各機構正討論相關計劃對市場的影響。<br />\n<br />\n消息<strong>拖累</strong>阿里巴巴和騰訊ADR，都較本港收市跌4%。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普簽署行政命令，禁止使用8個中國公司的應用程式，包括支付寶和微信支付等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569063-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569063-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5v3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=ced861df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569063-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d8c496a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569063-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2843c563d50f896d2550d2889913985fe9efb269","tid":2356481,"uid":3357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:26:38.000Z","msg":"彈出又彈入<br />\n彈入又彈出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a568be2751c8177a7684864db751cd29a49012a","tid":2356481,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b6e931a417085bd6b0ec25c57059fc47ed7c8d","tid":2356481,"uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:28:22.000Z","msg":"麵麵<img src=\"/